Titolo: Bush Hockey League

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Bush Hockey League (formerly Old Time Hockey) is an ice hockey video game for Windows and PlayStation 4. A version for Xbox One was released on 29 November 2017. A version for the Nintendo Switch was initially planned but later cancelled. The game is developed and published by V7 Entertainment.
The game draws inspiration from the 1977 film Slap Shot, and makes multiple references to the film's characters and teams.



Genere: Sport

Valutazione: 51
